Comment: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,op
Comment: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最後一次換齒輪軸是在什麼時候?
Comment: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,六天前的掃蕩作戰之後
Comment: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟紀錄一樣
Comment: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好 下一個
Comment: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,換妳了
Comment: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隸屬於41班
Comment: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,克里斯塔．連茲
Comment: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,查看她裝備的磨損
Comment: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連殺死巨人也要受懲罰呢...
Comment: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然有點怪 但那畢竟是很珍貴的實驗對象
Comment: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算如此為什麼只在我們訓練兵裡頭找犯人
Comment: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家光忙著處理戰場的善後都快累死了
Comment: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人實在是太可惡了 沒辦法
Comment: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是這樣一來就好像是幫了巨人似地
Comment: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許滿足了那個人的復仇心理
Comment: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對人類來說卻是個打擊
Comment: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我是個笨蛋 感覺稍微能夠理解...
Comment: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在我親眼見到巨人之前
Comment: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我很認真想要加入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 我現在連看都不想再看到
Comment: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明今天就得決定要加入哪個軍團
Comment: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰那傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是認真的...
Comment: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家都在後悔
Comment: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果早知道是這樣的地獄
Comment: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就不會選擇來當士兵
Comment: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在精疲力竭的現在
Comment: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我腦袋裡只有想到這個
Comment: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唉 馬可...
Comment: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經不知道哪一個才是你的骨頭了
Comment: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果沒有成為士兵的話
Comment: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就不用去想下一個變成這樣的人會是誰了
Comment: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道要放棄我們幾十萬人的犧牲 所換來的戰術上的進步
Comment: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後乖乖地去當巨人的食物嗎?
Comment: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道
Comment: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不戰鬥是不行的
Comment: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是每一個人都能成為像你一樣想找死的人
Comment: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不要生氣 先聽我說
Comment: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為約翰你並不是堅強的人
Comment: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以很能夠了解弱小的人的心情
Comment: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是因為這樣
Comment: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才能夠好好了解現狀並明確地行動
Comment: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在...
Comment: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我該做什麼...
Comment: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 我說你們
Comment: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們決定好隸屬的軍團了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可決定好了
Comment: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要加入調查軍團!
Comment: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡
Comment: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸 亞妮
Comment: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我之前就在想
Comment: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個約翰竟然說要加入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說約翰!?
Comment: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無所謂
Comment: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳是選憲兵團對吧?
Comment: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是不是也選妳那邊比較好?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說你
Comment: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果有人要你去死 你會去嗎?
Comment: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才不會去死
Comment: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼就順從自己的意思不就好了
Comment: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你又如何呢
Comment: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果理解了要為何而死的話
Comment: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認為有時候還是必須死去
Comment: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然不願意
Comment: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喔... 已經決定啦...
Comment: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然以前就有這樣子的打算
Comment: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真假 阿爾敏就連你也...
Comment: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看你好像很弱其實還挺有骨氣的
Comment: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝... 謝謝...
Comment: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞妮... 其實相當溫柔呢
Comment: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯?
Comment: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為妳好像不希望我們加入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳想加入憲兵團好像也有什麼理由不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有...
Comment: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是...
Comment: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想讓自己脫離苦海而已
Comment: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結果還是沒找到擅自使用立體機動裝置的士兵
Comment: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底是哪個傢伙幹的
Comment: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿災
Comment: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我現在倒比較擔心之後的新兵招募儀式
Comment: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底會有多少想入團的瘋狂新兵
Comment: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 艾連
Comment: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟你同期的有人會自願加入嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有啊
Comment: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原本是有...
Comment: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在如何就不清楚了
Comment: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,集合!
Comment: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點準備好
Comment: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要去說明會囉
Comment: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的!
Comment: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,早安 里維士官長
Comment: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽好了艾連
Comment: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要比我慢超過兩隻馬的距離喔
Comment: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別忘了都是因為我在「監視」著你 你才能過這麼悠哉
Comment: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走了!
Comment: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你真的要加入調查軍團?
Comment: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Comment: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼這麼突然
Comment: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個...難道你不會怕嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤? 廢話我當然討厭死調查軍團了
Comment: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 你又是為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我並不是因為覺得巨人不可怕才這樣子決定
Comment: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且有能力的人就該加入調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種話我也沒打算要說
Comment: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟想找死的人不一樣
Comment: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連嗎...
Comment: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙早就分配到調查軍團了吧
Comment: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,訓練兵們
Comment: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,列隊!
