Comment: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你變成巨人的時候
Comment: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,似乎打算把米卡莎給殺了
Comment: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎麼一回事?
Comment: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是這樣的 艾連他只是想要打蒼蠅...
Comment: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒有在問妳
Comment: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎 妳臉上的傷似乎很深
Comment: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是什麼時候受的傷?
Comment: 0,0:19:47.81,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,似乎是真的
Comment: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,變成巨人的我
Comment: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打算把米卡莎給殺了
Comment: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說「似乎」也就是說你沒有記憶的意思?
Comment: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說你對巨人力量存在到現在才知道
Comment: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連控制的力量也沒有
Comment: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 是的
Comment: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們聽到了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這似乎就是現狀
Comment: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們跟人類們的生命就託付給這傢伙了
Comment: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們就像馬可一樣
Comment: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會在艾連不知道的情況下死去吧
Comment: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰 你在這裡逼迫艾連有什麼意義?
Comment: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說啊 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是誰都像你一樣為了艾連可以無償的去死
Comment: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們應該要知道
Comment: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們是為了什麼 而賭上自己的生命
Comment: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然在緊要關頭會有所猶豫
Comment: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們祈求艾連可以給予我們保證
Comment: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓我們有確實的價值
Comment: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,才能正視...我們的生命
Comment: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以艾連!
Comment: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說你...真的...拜託你了
Comment: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好...
Comment: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,團長 即將出發了
Comment: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,附近的巨人都已經遠離了!
Comment: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開門前三十秒!
Comment: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,背上的標誌叫做自由之翼唷
Comment: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好帥喔
Comment: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,時候終於到了!!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,接下來人類將會再往前邁進一步!
Comment: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,展現你們訓練的成果吧!
Comment: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開始開門作業!
Comment: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前進!!
Comment: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第57次
Comment: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆外調查開始!
Comment: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,向前邁進!!
Comment: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,展開長距離搜索陣形向牆外前進的調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在他們面前突然出現的是...
Comment: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,擁有智慧的...
Comment: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謎之巨人
